{{Top|leg}}
The '''dedicated energy receptor projector''', or '''DER Projector''', was a component of the [[4x-Phantom Short-Range Sensor Jammer/Legends|4x-Phantom Short-Range Sensor Jammer]] utilized aboard the [[RZ-1 A-wing interceptor/Legends|RZ-1 A-wing interceptor]] manufactured by [[Miradyne Limited]]. It worked by absorbing and blocking incoming long-range sensor pings and transmissions broadcast by enemy ships, rendering the [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] invisible to most enemy scanners, [[Targeting computer/Legends|targeting computers]], and incoming [[Missile/Legends|missiles]].<ref name="EGWT">''[[The Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref>

